        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": "#IDB Projects and Programs Dataset \nThis dataset provides information on IDB projects and programs that are in preparation or have been approved to support the IDB’s 26 borrowing member countries.\nIt covers sovereign- and non-sovereign-guaranteed operations, including credit lines, lending facilities, grant financing facilities, financing programs, loans, guarantees, investment grants, technical cooperation, and equity investments. The dataset includes records from 1960 to the present, offering a long-term view of IDB financing activity across borrowing member countries.",
            "descriptionType": "Other"
          }
